OL,3,C'He has stolen my innocence' -
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks out about abuse as a
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,FA man has been sentenced to a decade
OL,8,Fin prison after being convicted of a
OL,9,Fstring of non-recent child sex
OL,10,Foffences.
OL,12,FScott Sly raped and sexually assaulted
OL,13,Fthe school-aged girl a number of times
OL,14,Fin the Sunderland area more than 20
OL,15,Fyears ago.
OL,17,FThe survivor came forward and reported
OL,18,Fthe abuse to police years later.
