OL,3,C'He has stolen my innocence' -
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks out about abuse as a
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,FThe now 32-year-old denied the
OL,8,Fallegations in interview but was
OL,9,Fcharged in January 2023.
OL,11,FIn March, Sly, of Dent Street,
OL,12,FHartlepool, appeared before Newcastle
OL,13,FCrown Court where he was found guilty
OL,14,Fby a jury of all 10 offences,
OL,15,Fincluding rape, indecent assault, and
OL,16,Fsexual assault.
OL,18,FAnd on Friday 14 June, he was
OL,19,Fsentenced to 10 years in prison at the
OL,20,Fsame court.
