OL,7,FHe will also spend the rest of his
OL,8,Flife on the Sex Offenders' Register
OL,9,Fand his victim will be protected by a
OL,10,Frestraining order.
OL,12,FTalking about the abuse, the survivor
OL,13,Fsaid: "It is hard to put into words
OL,14,Fexactly what effect this abuse has had
OL,15,Fon me, but I will try.
OL,17,F"This has impacted on my life every
OL,18,Fday since the abuse ` he has stolen my
OL,19,Finnocence.
