OL,7,FDetective Constable Nicholas Moses, of
OL,8,FNorthumbria Police's Safeguarding
OL,9,FDepartment, said: "I would like to
OL,10,Fexpress my complete respect to the
OL,11,Fsurvivor in this case who very bravely
OL,12,Fcame forward to disclose the abuse she
OL,13,Fsuffered at the hands of Sly.
OL,15,F"It's not an easy thing to come
OL,16,Fforward and have to re-live the worst
OL,17,Fmoments of your life but, thanks to
OL,18,Fher courage, Sly is now behind bars.
